Use Case 1: Upload Grocery Image

Actor: User (Home Cook / Student / Working Professional)

Precondition:
User has access to the CookSnap system.

Main Flow:

User selects the option to upload a grocery image.

System accepts the uploaded image.

Image is stored for processing.

Upload confirmation is displayed to the user.

Alternative Flow:

If the image format is unsupported or upload fails, the system displays an error message.

Postcondition:
A valid grocery image is successfully uploaded to the system.

Use Case 2: Get Recipe Recommendations

Actor: User

Precondition:
Grocery image is uploaded and ingredients are detected.

Main Flow:

User requests recipe recommendations.

System analyzes the detected ingredients.

System matches ingredients with available recipes.

Recommended recipes are displayed to the user.

Alternative Flow:

If no matching recipes are found, the system displays an appropriate message.

Postcondition:
User receives a list of suitable recipe recommendations.

Use Case 3: Monitor System Usage

Actor: Admin (System Administrator)

Precondition:
Admin is authenticated.

Main Flow:

Admin accesses the admin dashboard.

System displays system usage statistics and reports.

Admin reviews overall system performance.

Alternative Flow:

If no usage data is available, the system displays default values.

Postcondition:
System usage and performance are successfully monitored.
